movie.title: Hyde Park on Hudson
movie.plot: The story of the love affair between FDR and his distant cousin Margaret Stuckley, centered around the weekend in 1939 when the King and Queen of the United Kingdom visited upstate New York.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 1 win & 4 nominations.
